@page
@model AboutModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
}

<div class="about-container">
    <h1>ABOUT LCS PLAGIARISM CHECKER</h1>
    <p>
        This tool uses the Longest Common Subsequence (LCS) algorithm to find the longest sequence of words that appear in the same order in both texts.
    </p>
    <p>
        The similarity score is calculated using the Sørensen–Dice coefficient, adapted for LCS:
    </p>
    <pre>Similarity % = (2 * LCS_Length) / (Length_of_Text1 + Length_of_Text2) * 100</pre>
    <p>
        The tool breaks text down into tokens by removing punctuation and splitting by whitespace.
        It then computes the optimal sequence using dynamic programming.
        This provides a fair, symmetric metric for natural language text comparison.
    </p>
</div>
